<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('head.ejs') %>
  </head>
    <body id="page-top">
        <%- include('navigation.ejs') %>
        <br><br><br>
        <!-- Check Section-->
        <section class="page-section" id="contact">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- Check Section Heading-->
                <h2 class="page-section-heading text-center text-uppercase text-secondary mb-0">자가진단</h2>
                <!-- Icon Divider-->
                <div class="divider-custom">
                    <div class="divider-custom-line"></div>
                    <div class="divider-custom-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
                    <div class="divider-custom-line"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Check Section Form-->
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <!-- To configure the contact form email address, go to mail/contact_me.php and update the email address in the PHP file on line 19.-->
                        <form id="contactForm" name="sentMessage" novalidate="novalidate">
                            <div id="self">
                            <div class="form-group " style="text-align:left">
                                <h6>1. 최근 5년이내 입원한 경험이 있나요?</h6>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="admission" value="yes" >Yes</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="admission" value="no">No</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group " style="text-align:left">
                                <h6>2. 하루에 얼마나 흡연하시나요?</h6> 
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="smoke" value="0">아예 안함</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="smoke" value="1">1~5개피</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="smoke" value="2">6~15개피</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="smoke" value="3">16~20개피</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="smoke" value="4">1갑 이상</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group " style="text-align:left">
                                <h6>3. 음주량은 어느 정도인가요?</h6>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="drink" value="0">아예 안함</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="drink" value="1">1잔~5잔</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="drink" value="2">6잔~15잔</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="drink" value="3">1병이상</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="drink" value="4">3병 이상</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group " style="text-align:left">
                                <h6>4. 가족력 질환이 있으신가요?</h6>
                                <input type="text" name="disease" >
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group " style="text-align:left">
                                <h6>4. 해당 되는 생활습관에 체크해주세요.</h6>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="habit" value="0">코를 심하게 곤다.</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="habit" value="1">불끄고 스마트폰을 본다.</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="habit" value="2">눈을 자주 비빈다.</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="habit" value="3">야외활동을 자주 하지 않는다.</label>
                                <br>
                                <label><input type="checkbox" name="habit" value="4">한쪽으로만 가방을 든다.</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                            <div id="down">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <a class="btn btn-xl btn-primary" style="width: 100%;" href="check">
                                    결과보기
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('footer.ejs') %>
        <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <!-- Third party plugin JS-->
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-easing/1.4.1/jquery.easing.min.js"></script>
        <!-- Contact form JS-->
        <script src="assets/mail/jqBootstrapValidation.js"></script>
        <!-- Core theme JS-->
        <script src="js/scripts.js"></script>

  </body>
</html>

